5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg>Encrypted Inquiry</button></a><a href="/contact"><button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 transition-colors h-8 px-3 text-xs rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground border border-primary-border hover:bg-primary/90 shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:shadow-xl" aria-label="Get a Quote"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-phone w-4 h-4"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>Get a Quote</button></a></div><button id="mobile-menu-toggle" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobile-menu" class="md:hidden p-2 text-slate-600" aria-label="Toggle menu"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6"><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="6" y2="6"></line><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="18" y2="18"></line></svg></button></div><div id="mobile-menu" class="md:hidden hidden border-t border-slate-200 bg-white" aria-hidden="true"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex flex-col gap-3"><a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Home</a><a href="/services" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Services</a><a href="/about" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">About</a><a href="/blog" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Field Notes</a><a href="/contact" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Contact</a><a href="/contact" class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium rounded-md border border-emerald-500/50 text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50 min-h-8 px-3 text-xs py-2">Encrypted Inquiry</a><a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground min-h-8 px-3 text-xs py-2">Get a Quote</a></div></div></nav><main class="flex-grow"><section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-44 md:pb-24 overflow-hidden bg-slate-50"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div><div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-primary/5 to-transparent skew-x-12 transform origin-top-right translate-x-32"></div><div class="container relative mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 z-10 max-w-4xl"><span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-primary/20 animate-fade-in-up">Pricing</span><h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-[1.1] mb-6 animate-fade-in-up delay-1">What it costs, <span class="text-primary">before we get on a call.</span></h1><p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-4 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up delay-2">We'd rather you know up front whether we're affordable than waste your time on a sales call. Here are the ranges. Specific quotes follow the intake conversation; nothing on this page is a binding offer.</p></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white text-slate-900"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-4xl"><div class="space-y-12"><div class="reveal"><div class="mb-4"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-xl text-slate-900">Hourly engagements</h2></div><div class="mb-4"><p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-600">For ongoing work without a fixed scope: configuration changes, incident response, ad-hoc audits.</p></div><p class="text-slate-900 font-semibold text-2xl mb-2">$185 – $275 / hour</p><p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Senior engineer rate. Higher end for after-hours / weekend / on-call. Tracked in 15-minute increments. Invoiced monthly with itemized work log.</p></div><div class="reveal"><div class="mb-4"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-xl text-slate-900">Retainer engagements</h2></div><div class="mb-4"><p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-600">Predictable monthly cost for ongoing operational support — patching, monitoring, periodic audit prep.</p></div><p class="text-slate-900 font-semibold text-2xl mb-2">$2,500 – $9,500 / month</p><p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Sized to staff count + service surface. Includes a fixed hour bucket; overflow at the standard hourly rate. 30-day cancellation; no long-term lock-in.</p></div><div class="reveal"><div class="mb-4"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-xl text-slate-900">Fixed-scope projects</h2></div><div class="mb-4"><p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-600">For one-time deliverables with a clear shape: cloud migration, mail server self-hosting, security audit + remediation, vertical-specific compliance posture.</p></div><p class="text-slate-900 font-semibold text-2xl mb-2">$8,000 – $60,000 per project</p><p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Quoted after a paid discovery (typically $1,500 – $3,000, credited toward the project if you hire us). Discovery deliverable is yours regardless — you can take it elsewhere.</p></div><div class="reveal"><div class="mb-4"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-xl text-slate-900">Discovery / scoping</h2></div><div class="mb-4"><p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-600">When the shape is unclear or you're shopping vendors. We produce a written assessment of your current state, top three risks, and a recommended next-step plan.</p></div><p class="text-slate-900 font-semibold text-2xl mb-2">$1,500 – $3,000, fixed</p><p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Two-week turnaround. Yours to keep regardless of next steps.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-slate-50 text-slate-900"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-4xl"><div class="reveal"><div class="mb-6"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-3xl md:text-4xl text-slate-900">What we don't do</h2></div><ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-700 text-lg"><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span><strong>No &quot;call for pricing.&quot; </strong>If we're a bad fit on price, you should know in 30 seconds, not three phone calls.</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span><strong>No bait-and-switch. </strong>The proposal we send is what you pay; scope changes require a written change order with a new price.</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span><strong>No long-term lock-in. </strong>Retainers are 30-day cancellable. We'd rather earn renewal than collect a termination fee.</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span><strong>No referral kickbacks. </strong>When we recommend a third-party tool or vendor, we are not paid to do so. Recommendations are based on fit.</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span><strong>No license-arbitrage markup. </strong>If we resell software (Microsoft 365, etc.) we pass through at cost.</span></li></ul></div></div></section><section class="py-20 bg-slate-900 text-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-4xl"><div class="reveal"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white">If our rates don't fit, we'll tell you who does.</h2><div class="mt-6"><p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-slate-400">We're not a fit for every budget. If you're a 1-2 person practice that needs $50/month tier IT support, you should hire someone other than us — and we'll happily refer. The intake conversation is a free filter that protects your time as much as ours.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="py-20 bg-primary/5 text-slate-900"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-3xl"><div class="text-center reveal"><div class="mb-6"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-3xl md:text-4xl text-slate-900">Ready to talk numbers?</h2></div><a href="/contact"><button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 transition-colors h-12 px-8 py-6 text-lg rounded-xl bg-primary text-primary-foreground border border-primary-border hover:bg-primary/90 shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:shadow-xl" aria-label="Schedule an intake call">Schedule an intake call</button></a></div></div></section></main><footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 py-16"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12"><div class="space-y-6"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white"><div class="bg-primary p-1.5 rounded-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-6 h-6 text-white"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"/></svg></div><span class="font-display font-bold text-xl tracking-tight">PlausiDen <span class="text-primary">LLC</span></span></div><p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">Providing comprehensive, high-quality IT solutions that empower modern enterprises. General yet specific excellence in technology.</p></div><div class="space-y-6"><h3 class="text-white font-display font-semibold text-lg">Company</h3><ul class="space-y-3"><li><a href="/"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Home</span></a></li><li><a href="/about"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">About Us</span></a></li><li><a hr