 class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg><a href="tel:9783516495"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">978-351-6495</span></a></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg><a href="mailto:team@plausiden.com"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">team@plausiden.com</span></a></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg><span class="text-sm">Massachusetts, USA</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-slate-500"><p>© PlausiDen LLC. All rights reserved.</p><div class="flex gap-6"><a href="/privacy-directive"><span class="hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Sovereign Privacy Directive</span></a><a href="/terms-of-service"><span class="hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Sovereign Terms of Service</span></a></div></div></div></footer></div></div></body></html>
